Masujiro was a military scholar, Western scholar and doctor at the end of the Edo period and during the Meiji Restoration.
After teaching at Bansho Shirabesho, the shogunate's research and educational institution for Western studies, he opened a private school, Kyukyodo, in Edo, where he taught Western studies, military science, and medicine.
